Package com.blueparrott.blueparrottsdk

Interface BPHeadset

  • public interface BPHeadset
    Class used to get a handle to BlueParrott headset Connect, enable the SDK and add listeners for events

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field Description
      static int CONNECT_METHOD_AUTO
      Used with connect(int) to specify that SDK should detect best connection mode available - will attempt to connect over classic, and if that fails will connect over BLE
      static int CONNECT_METHOD_BLE
      Used with connect(int) to force connection over Bluetooth Low Energy
      static int CONNECT_METHOD_CLASSIC
      Used with connect(int) to force connection over Classic Bluetooth
